  "original_title": "Sri Lanka Comtrust rebrands to CT CLSA Asset Management",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka Comtrust rebrands to CT CLSA Asset Management",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka\u2019s Comtrust Asset Management, a fully owned subsidiary of CT CLSA Holdings has rebranded to CT CLSA Asset Management with effect from this month. to reposition the Company consistent with all business units under the single brand identity of CT CLSA, the firm said in a statement.",
        "\u201cThis would enable CT CLSA Asset Management to further establish itself within the industry with the direct association of strong local and international shareholders while upholding its key values of Commitment, Trust, and Continuity to all stakeholders,\u201d it said.",
        "\u201cThe rebranding reassures the commitment by the shareholders to the asset management business, and the continuous support to grow the asset management business to be a market leader in providing innovative wealth management solutions.\u201d",
        "The company believes that the rebranding would auger well to capitalize on the group synergies and cross sell opportunities across the group.",
        "The company said it has nurtured retail and high net worth investors over its 28 years journey and hopes to",
        "leverage its expertise to advice and enhance returns to its clients amidst the current macroeconomic",
        "CT CLSA Asset Management is a fully owned subsidiary of the CT CLSA Holdings Group and is a unit trust management company in Sri Lanka.",
        "The company manages Equity and Fixed Income Unit Trusts as well as offering Private Portfolio management solutions for both institutional and high net worth investors with varying investment objectives.",
        "CT CLSA Holdings is a capital market service provider in Sri Lanka offering investment banking, stockbroking and asset management services through its fully owned subsidiaries; CT CLSA Capital, CT CLSA Securities (a member of the Colombo Stock Exchange) and CT CLSA Asset Management.",
        "CT CLSA Holdings is a subsidiary of listed conglomerate, CT Holdings Group and the CLSA Group of Hong Kong. CLSA is one of Asia\u2019s largest investment groups and a fully owned subsidiary of CITIC Securities, China\u2019s largest investment bank."
      ],
